In BC, the list of persons eligible for the publicly funded (free) HPV9 vaccine is available here. If you do not meet the free criteria, the HPV vaccines can be purchased at most pharmacies and travel health clinics. Some health insurance plans may cover the cost of the vaccine; check with your insurance provider. Information about why all vaccines aren't free is here.
